{"tid":1561533,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"屌呀！914親子遊被popo反對","createTime":"2019-09-11T15:40:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T10:41:31.000Z","uid":108477,"like":132,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"bc4276851289409dac9ac239ec8c7b50f6122153","tid":1561533,"uid":108477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:40:21.000Z","msg":"【 警方就914遊行發出反對通知書】<br />\n<br />\n申請人於今日傍晚收到警方就914天水圍親子遊行發出的反對通知書， 以安全為理由反對當日所舉行的親子遊行。 主辦方對此表示遺憾，並譴責警方近日屢次反對遊行的申請是侵犯香港市民的遊行及集會自由。<br />\n<br />\n目前主辦方將就反對通知書提出上訴，亦考慮把遊行改為集會，其細節將於尋求法律意見後公佈。<br />\n<br />\n一如以往所提及，是次天水圍遊是為了提高區內居民對市民堅持五大訴求的認知，解釋何以在政府提出撤回條例修訂後仍堅持抗爭。過往主流媒體報導偏頗，令不少街坊對示威有誤解。是次活動正期望透過和平、理性、溫馨的遊行打破街坊對示威的誤解，進而增強雙方互諒。而我們深信，建立真正的溝通是民主社會必要的元素。<br />\n<br />\n雖然警方及政府屢屢打壓民眾表達訴求的權利，但永遠無法磨滅民眾的決心。<br />\n<br />\n一群關心香港的天水圍街坊上"},{"pid":"3138f88425ee68d941778e124f9ef7bf250f2b97","tid":1561533,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:41:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"86010402e59a870ec19dd6551fb72268e1d73ed6","tid":1561533,"uid":5682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:41:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"